Q11: Write a program to input an integer and check whether it is even or odd using ifâ€“else.

/*
Sample Test Cases:
Input 1:
7
Output 1:
7 is odd

Input 2:
12
Output 2:
12 is even

*/

  #include <stdio.h>
int main(){
    int n;
    printf("Enter any integer: ");
    scanf("%d", &n);

    if(n % 2 == 0)
        printf("It is an even number.");
    else
    printf("It is an odd number.");
    
    return 0;
}
